Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Central Limit Theorem
Formula: Sample means → normal distribution
Note:    Foundation of statistical inference and polling

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Central Dogma
Formula: DNA → RNA → Protein
Note:    Information flow in all living organisms

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Speed of Light
Formula: c = 299,792,458 m/s in vacuum
Note:    Foundation of special relativity; universal speed limit

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   ATP
Formula: ADP + Pi → ATP
Note:    Universal energy currency of all living cells

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Bayes Theorem
Formula: P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)
Note:    Updating probability based on new evidence

